  "format": "Sean, Amanda, and Chris Ryan draft action set pieces instead of movies: two scenes per host across the '80s, '90s, 2000s, 2010s, 2020s, and a wildcard round, from the Die Hard fire-hose jump to Paul riding the sandworm.",
  "segments": [
